city kids how to read,

01:57.576 --> 01:59.158
but then I was like... (BLOWS
RASPBERRY) This is my Saturday.

01:59.453 --> 02:01.444
Awesome. Well, the
girls got their stupid thing,

02:01.747 --> 02:04.205
