(SINGSONGY) That's Roy...

13:55.877 --> 13:56.742
On!
(JANE) There he is!

13:57.045 --> 13:58.035
Hi! He ; y, Roys R Us!

13:58.338 --> 14:00.204
Ah! Hello, ladies.
(DOOR CLOSES)

14:00.506 --> 14:01.462
