but it's outside of our budget.

14:14.479 --> 14:16.436
Well, no, money's
No object. | got it.

14:16.731 --> 14:19.814
Penny, the Drake is the best
place to get married in Chicago.

14:20.109 --> 14:22.020
| mean, Oprah and Stedman
have had it reserved for 17 years.

14:22.320 --> 14:23.685
Okay, slow down.

14:23.988 --> 14:25.899
Pete and I are very happy with
the wedding we have planned.

14:26.199 --> 14:27.815
Speaking of Pete,

14:28.117 --> 14:31.075
