future father-in-law

14:32.663 --> 14:34.153
kind of thing to do,
you know?

14:34.457 --> 14:36.118
Do you think it's too soon
to ask him to call me Dad?

14:37.418 --> 14:39.284
Yeah, Roy. I do.

14:39.587 --> 14:40.918
| don't even call you
Dad... (CHUCKLES)

14:41.214 --> 14:43.080
