punched me in the face at prom.

14:56.771 --> 14:58.512
And I know it only seems like
| needed you during dances,

14:58.815 --> 15:00.681
but there were plenty
of other times, too.

15:01.943 --> 15:03.149
| don't know...
(SIGHS) Roy.

15:05.863 --> 15:07.024
Maybe this whole thing
was a mistake.

15:09.200 --> 15:10.611
Well...

15:10.910 --> 15:12.992
I'm sorry
that you feel that way.

15:13.287 --> 15:15.654
(SIGHS) Maybe I should just
go back to New York.

15:16.874 --> 15:17.830
Yeah, maybe you should.

15:28.177 --> 15:30.043
Guys, this could be
the bellinis talking,

15:30.346 --> 15:31.928
