15:44.986 --> 15:46.226
(SAMBA MUSIC PLAYING)

15:54.954 --> 15:57.116
The Brazilian stole
Dave's idea.

15:57.415 --> 15:59.156
| don't know. | mean, people
develop the same idea all the time

15:59.459 --> 16:00.494
without two guys having sex
with each other.

16:00.793 --> 16:02.375
What?

16:02.670 --> 16:04.957
Look, I saw Wilson last night,
and I gave up the goods.

16:05.256 --> 16:06.337
