16:14.891 --> 16:16.131
You know the one thing
we haven't tried yet?

16:16.434 --> 16:17.265
Bees. Smart.

16:17.560 --> 16:18.925
No, Max, talking.

16:19.228 --> 16:20.468
All right?
I'm an adult.

16:20.771 --> 16:22.227
