really wanna samba.

16:31.407 --> 16:32.568
(WHISPERS) I know.

16:35.244 --> 16:36.234
| get it.

16:39.999 --> 16:41.285
Hello, the Brazilian.

16:43.628 --> 16:45.460
Hello, the American.

16:45.755 --> 16:46.790
| made you this sandwich
as a peace offering.

16:48.090 --> 16:49.421
We gotta end
this madness.

16:49.717 --> 16:51.333
We must figure out a way
to share Wrigleyville.

16:51.636 --> 16:53.092
You're right.

16:53.387 --> 16:54.843
Come back
after closing.

16:55.139 --> 16:58.097
We'll talk it out
over a cafe con leche.

16:58.935 --> 17:00.801
Okay.

17:01.103 --> 17:01.592
(IMITATES BRAZILIAN ACCENT)
Cafe con leche.

17:01.896 --> 17:02.806
Sim.
Okay.

17:04.607 --> 17:05.813
Nailed it, David.

17:10.445 --> 17:11.356
Really?

17:12.573 --> 17:13.404
Ooh!

17:18.538 --> 17:20.119
(ALL SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY)

17:24.710 --> 17:25.619
Ah!

17:27.255 --> 17:28.086
Ah!

17:29.423 --> 17:30.413
Yes!

17:30.716 --> 17:31.330
Oh!

17:33.052 --> 17:33.962
(SHOUTS INDISTINCTLY)

17:35.388 --> 17:36.173
Ah!

17:40.518 --> 17:41.553
(SCREECHES)

17:41.852 --> 17:42.683
Get a shirt!

17:42.979 --> 17:43.764
Ah!

17:48.568 --> 17:49.979
(SLOW MOTION VOICE) Oh!

18:16.304 --> 18:17.794
No!

18:21.017 --> 18:22.633
(PENNY SHRIEKS)

18:22.935 --> 18:24.141
Roy?

18:24.437 --> 18:25.393
(GASPS)
