You stole Dave's idea!

18:38.326 --> 18:40.192
I'm sorry! My father
invoked "dads before lads!"

18:40.494 --> 18:41.984
| couldn't argue
with that.

18:42.288 --> 18:43.369
For what it's worth,
| really liked you.

18:43.664 --> 18:44.745
| really liked you, too.

18:45.041 --> 18:45.906
