19:06.145 --> 19:07.852
We must find a way
to work in peace, Dan.

19:08.522 --> 19:10.263
It's Dave.

19:10.566 --> 19:11.806
| work pretty hard
not to look like a Dan.

19:13.069 --> 19:13.934
Respect.

19:15.821 --> 19:17.232
